svg.source: Title: Invite Guest to Exchange Event User-->User Interface: Click Invite button User Interface-->User: Display Invite Page User-->User Interface: Enters Data and Submit User Interface-->User Interface: Validates Data Note right of User Interface: If error, display message User Interface-->Server API: Calls send invite API Server API-->Server API: Validates Data Note right of Server API: If error, return with error Server API-->Database: Save new invite Database-->Server API: Saved invite Server API-->Email Platform: Send invite email Server API-->User Interface: Saved invite json User Interface-->User Interface: Show success message User Interface-->User: Redirect to the event page
